{"tid":1167412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中美貿易戰】中國美國商會調查　逾四成受訪外資考慮生產線撤出中國","createTime":"2019-05-23T04:36:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T11:05:18.000Z","uid":141151,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a946a891fa713d0004ecc12adb0e457413e5c55a","tid":1167412,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T04:36:34.000Z","msg":"【中美貿易戰】中國美國商會調查　逾四成受訪外資考慮生產線撤出中國<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%95%86%E6%9C%83%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-%E9%80%BE%E5%9B%9B%E6%88%90%E5%8F%97%E8%A8%AA%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%87%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2%E7%B7%9A%E6%92%A4%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%2588%25B0-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5-%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%258F%2597%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25B3%2587%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2594%25A2%25E7%25B7%259A%25E6%2592%25A4%25E5%2587%25BA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyowpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=33fee920\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%2588%25B0-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5-%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%258F%2597%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25B3%2587%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2594%25A2%25E7%25B7%259A%25E6%2592%25A4%25E5%2587%25BA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F&h=f463c310\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%95%86%E6%9C%83%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-%E9%80%BE%E5%9B%9B%E6%88%90%E5%8F%97%E8%A8%AA%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%87%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2%E7%B7%9A%E6%92%A4%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/</a><br />\n<br />\n中美貿易磨擦持續，在中國的外資隨時「跳船」。中國美國商會與上海美國商會日前進行聯合調查，近 7 成半受訪會員表示中美互徵關稅，對業務構成負面影響，當中以製造業首當其衝，更有超過 4 成受訪會員，正考慮或已經將生產線遷出中國，3 分 1 會推遲或取消對華投資。<br />\n<br />\n兩間商會於本月 16 至 20 日聯合調查，評估中美互徵關稅對外資在中國業務的影響，收到近 250 份回覆，調查顯示 74.9% 受訪外資生意受中美貿易戰負面影響，更有 40.7% 的受訪者表示，正考慮或已經將生產線遷出中國，有四分一考慮將生產線遷往東南亞，33.2% 外資表示會推遲和取消對華投資。<br />\n<br />\n除了撤出中國外，外資企業亦考慮將中國生產的貨品在當地銷售，約 35.3% 企業表示會採取「中國製造，中國銷售」(In China, for China)策略；雖然過半受訪企業表示，未見到中國政府有採取非關稅報復措施，但部分受訪外資表示，感覺中方有增加檢查、減慢過關速度、增加審查和減慢批准申請速度等。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中美角力持續，已陸續有外資將生產線撤出中國，美國運動攝影機製造商 GoPro 將在今年夏天前，搬走大部分輸往美國產品的生產線；Sony 亦於 3 月宣佈，關閉北京手機廠，將生產線遷至泰國。</span></span>"},{"pid":"b44525abbc07b82f923571df2996af47e6621015","tid":1167412,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T04:37:51.000Z","msg":"華為都已經考慮將美國工廠撤走"},{"pid":"a80d6e2920a4b92c601b4757bfc97abf9e62c408","tid":1167412,"uid":56123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T04:42:01.000Z","msg":"東南亞發大財了"},{"pid":"dc5d2b58135f44299b6a345e675f8c0b6ff016b5","tid":1167412,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T04:43:15.000Z","msg":"美國平民成最大輸家<br />\n中國成最大贏家"},{"pid":"0bec174dd347bcaf08cbd723a88621d7b8bfdfb9","tid":1167412,"uid":101945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T04:46:32.000Z","msg":"中國靠炒樓咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n洗咩靠工廠"},{"pid":"49fed96ca7c5036416f16731f5da60ed3c3a453b","tid":1167412,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T23:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67d948f7938d1b2ecee1d8edb233d968dee6d16","tid":1167412,"uid":35580,"